    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable daily driver that\u2019s full of heart? This car has been a faithful companion and still has plenty of life left in it! It shows some honest signs of its journey with some cosmetic marks and typical wear, but it remains a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a great value. It\u2019s been well-maintained where it counts and is eager to hit the road with its next owner!",
