      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in showroom-level condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and possessing a flawless mechanical pedigree. Every detail, from the immaculate interior to the pristine exterior finish, confirms its status as a premier investment for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
